title: Hits Of M.M.Kreem (2007)(gnv64)
description:
Koduri Keeravaani, better known as M. M. Keeravaani under the alias Maragatha Mani (Tamil Cinema) and M. M. Kreem (Bollywood), is an Indian film music composer and Playback singer, who works in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam and Hindi cinema. In 1997, he has garnered the National
Film Award for Best Music Direction. He has won eight Andhra Pradesh state Nandi Awards, four Filmfare Awards South and a Tamil Nadu State Film Award. He was priveleged to work with legendary veterans like K. Vishwanath, K. Balachander and Bharathan very early in his career.
